Introduction

Yebin is a South Korean singer-songwriter under Yam Yam Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group DIA and its sub-unit BCHCS and a former member of the project girl group UNI.T.

On September 14, 2015, she debuted as a member of the girl group DIA with the release of their first studio album Do It Amazing.

In 2017, she joined KBS 2TV's idol rebooting survival show The Unit, alongside fellow member Somyi. Considered as the most charming personality during the show, she ranked 2nd place, thus becoming part of the female unit, UNI.T. The group debuted on May 18, 2018 with the mini album Line.

On June 23, 2021 Yebin announced that she would be making her solo debut with her first digital single, "Yes I Know" on July 7.
